law.history: Repealed 1974 Ky. Acts ch. 406, sec. 336, effective January 1, 1975. -- Created 1956 Ky. Acts ch. 244, sec. 3, effective May 18, 1956.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Selling, lending, showing, advertising for sale or distribution to persons under the age of eighteen years of comic books described under KRS 436.550 -- Presumptive evidence.
